title: Relaxation - Sounds of the Earth: Wadden - Sands and Seagulls
description:
Sounds of the Earth:

Wadden - Sands and Seagulls

--------------------

The Wadden are said to be the Nursery of the North Sea. And indeed,
although the tide moves in its everlasting slow rhythm and one can
sometimes actually hear the silence of the Wadden, the sea and the
sands are full of life.

Total Time: 53:52

---

Sounds of the Earth offers pure nature sounds, no voices are
added, no music is added, no human-induced noises are heard.
Sounds of the Earth bids you welcome to the wild and the
fragile sounds of nature.

---

Enjoy!
